<plot>Elena, twenty years old, gets home at night after fighting with her boyfriend. Somebody, something follows her back home and inside each room. There is a broken pendulum-clock near the family's pictures, the television is on but without signal. Yes, there is somebody, something. And now even mirrors are fearful.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?392728</url></doc>
